items.title: Police arrest suspects for armed robbery, drug peddling in Abuja
items.summary: "The arrested suspects include: Manaseh Emmanuel (36), Dogora Ibrahim (21), and Ibrahim Idamusa (40), who are members of a notorious armed robbery gang
